          width="360px"
          alt="Welcome to an exciting new connection."
          href="https://www.audiusa.com/us/web/en/inside-audi/innovation/audi-connect.html?csref=%%=v(@csrefTagBase)=%%Hero_ExcitingConnectionsImg"
          target="_blank"
